{"tid":1091550,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"約左條臭雞食飯","createTime":"2019-04-04T08:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T12:00:49.000Z","uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4b41e67b4a2844e2d5fb58e5d4bdb329e81706","tid":1091550,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"太忙冇乜點打扮 求其著件褸就出左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女見我著到咁寒酸 全程玩電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到埋單嗰陣 我舉手叫waiter過黎 露左隻ap出黎<br />\n條女對眼即刻發晒光 仲問我係咪撈黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都廢事理佢 <br />\n即刻叫工人揸架McLaren過黎畀我兜下風<br />\n拎張黑卡出黎嗰陣 條女猛咁拉低件衫<br />\n明明頭先仲話凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後畀左1000工人同條女各自搭的士返屋企<br />\n唔知夠唔夠錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家就自己揸左上山頂開呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933c12d32bfa340ecf3773378468da69916207ee","tid":1091550,"uid":21355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱訓醒就開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b45bb937fff07faf0a60282dce8273468af764","tid":1091550,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"933c12d32bfa340ecf3773378468da69916207ee","tid":1091550,"uid":21355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱訓醒就開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"一早醒左 daddy話有單生意畀我試下傾<br />\n點知朝早就傾成左 uncle仲讚我叻仔<br />\n所以咪約條女食下飯囉"},{"pid":"222605330f71ace7c0af6d67a44b036726b6a663","tid":1091550,"uid":146299,"like":